      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">Software</a> * Tournament Manager</b>\n</p><p><b>Tournament Manager</b>,<br />\nprograms and scripts, often incorporated in <a href=\"/User_Interface\" title=\"User Interface\">user Interfaces</a>, to play automated chess engine <a href=\"/Tournaments_and_Matches\" title=\"Tournaments and Matches\">tournaments</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Programs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Programs\">Programs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tournament_Manager&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Programs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Amoeba#TournamentManager\" title=\"Amoeba\">Amoeba Tournament Manager</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Banksia\" title=\"Banksia\">Banksia</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/C-chess-cli\" title=\"C-chess-cli\">c-chess-cli</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=CETSA&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"CETSA (page does not exist)\">CETSA</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessGUI\" title=\"ChessGUI\">ChessGUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Cute_Chess\" title=\"Cute Chess\">Cute Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=FSTM&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"FSTM (page does not exist)\">FSTM</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/LittleBlitzer\" title=\"LittleBlitzer\">LittleBlitzer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Lucas_Chess\" title=\"Lucas Chess\">Lucas Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Scid_vs._PC\" title=\"Scid vs. PC\">Scid vs. PC</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WinBoard#TournamentManager\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/XBoard#TournamentManager\" title=\"XBoard\">XBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tournament_Manager&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Auto232\" title=\"Auto232\">Auto232</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bayeselo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bayeselo (page does not exist)\">Bayeselo</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chess_Server\" title=\"Chess Server\">Chess Server</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Elostat&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Elostat (page does not exist)\">Elostat</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Engine_Rating_Lists\" title=\"Engine Rating Lists\">Engine Rating Lists</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/OpenBench\" title=\"OpenBench\">OpenBench</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ordo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ordo (page does not exist)\">Ordo</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">Protocols</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Web_Broadcast\" title=\"Web Broadcast\">Web Broadcast</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tournament_Manager&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62922\">sprt tourney manager</a> by <a href=\"/Richard_Delorme\" title=\"Richard Delorme\">Richard Delorme</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Amoeba#TournamentManager\" title=\"Amoeba\">Amoeba Tournament Manager</a>, <a href=\"/Match_Statistics#SPRT\" title=\"Match Statistics\">SPRT</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77372\">CETSA (Chess Engine Tournament Script for Android)</a> by Archimedes, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 24, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Android\" title=\"Android\">Android</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tournament_Manager&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77372\">CETSA (Chess Engine Tournament Script for Android)</a> by Archimedes, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>